title: The Cheese Gang - JG, ADC + SUPP Wanted! (High silver - Low gold)
body:
*The Cheese Gang* is a team that focuses on fun, but always wants to rise the ranks.  So far its just two guys, but we're hoping for it to expand to a group with around 5 - 6 members. We need a Jungler, ADC, and Support in order to complete the team. Positive attitude required.
So far the members include:
Goragle (Silver III)
Jellytree (Silver II)
We're hoping to rise to gold as quickly as possible, and it would be great if we had a team to play with competitively and socially!
A preliminary game will be required to assess whether you're the right kind of person we are looking for. You don't have to be amazing - just play your best and keep a positive attitude!

Send Goragle or Jellytree a friend request if you're interested!

Good luck on the Fields of Justice! {{champion:86}}

replies.body:
All places have now been filled! Sorry if you didn't get placed, we got a lot of people flooding our inboxes and it was difficult to contact you all. Thanks for wanting to be a part of the team!

Good luck on the Fields of Justice! {{champion:86}}
